description:
Fire up your engine and unlock five of the most the powerful Asphalt beasts, along with a bag full of resources to help you on your path to becoming a Nintendo Switch™ legend.

The pack contains:
•         30 Blueprints to unlock the Ferrari F12tdf
•         45 Blueprints to unlock the Aston Martin Vulcan
•         40 Blueprints to unlock the SCG 003S
•         30 Blueprints to unlock the SIN R1 550
•         45 Blueprints to unlock the Dodge Viper GTS
•         300,000 Credits 
•         200 Tokens
name: Asphalt 9: Legends – High-Gear Pack
